== 片中瑣事 ==
* 在影片插曲：《Nachle Ve》當中，RV到[[C-Town|C-Town]]商場尋工作，他把一些商品從貨架上弄下地，老闆就把他辭退了，這個鏡頭一晃就過去，很容易被人忽略。
* 影片中一個女人提出付六百美金給RV，要他送她[[肯尼迪國境機場|肯尼迪國境機場]]趕飛機，實際上道具車開上了到[[紐瓦克自由國境機場|紐瓦克自由國境機場]]的道路，最後又停在該機場的場站大廳門外。<!-- While the movie is set in New York, there was actual talk of the [[International_Speedway_Corporation|International Speedway Corporation]] setting up a real 3/4 mile track in Staten Island;  those plans were later shelved.  The fictious track was actually [[Rockingham_Speedway|Rockingham Speedway]], a 1.017 mile oval in Rockingham, North Carolina.  Many of the cars used in the movie were owned by the Fast Track High Performance driving school, which now owns the track.  The school has frequently offered race cars for racing movies, and trains drivers for movies.  The cars used were ARCA Re/Max Series cars, and ARCA will race in 2008 at the track. -->
* 影片中一段事故翻車的鏡頭很像2004年的一次[[NASCAR_Subway_400|NASCAR Subway 400]]真實事故鏡頭重放，一些車迷看出了這一巧合，然而這的確純屬巧合。

